Title="UGREEN iDX6011 Pro"
Icon="hdd-o"
Markdown="true"
---
<?php
/* UGREEN iDX6011 Pro front-panel settings. Writes /update.php -> the plugin's
   panel/settings.cfg on flash, then restarts the dashboard (start-panel.sh). */
$plugin  = 'ugreen-idx6011-pro';
$cfgfile = "/boot/config/plugins/$plugin/panel/settings.cfg";
$cfg     = file_exists($cfgfile) ? (@parse_ini_file($cfgfile) ?: []) : [];
$val = function($k, $def = '') use ($cfg) { return isset($cfg[$k]) ? $cfg[$k] : $def; };

/* detect real network interfaces for the "primary" picker */
$ifaces = [];
foreach (glob('/sys/class/net/*') as $p) {
    $n = basename($p);
    if ($n === 'lo' || $n === 'bonding_masters') continue;
    if (preg_match('/^(veth|docker|tunl|sit|vnet|br-|dummy|wg)/', $n)) continue;
    $ifaces[] = $n;
}
sort($ifaces);

function opts($items, $cur) {
    foreach ($items as $v => $lbl)
        echo '<option value="' . htmlspecialchars($v) . '"' .
             ((string)$cur === (string)$v ? ' selected' : '') . '>' .
             htmlspecialchars($lbl) . '</option>';
}
?>
<form markdown="1" method="POST" action="/update.php" target="progressFrame">
<input type="hidden" name="#file" value="<?=$plugin?>/panel/settings.cfg">
<input type="hidden" name="#command" value="/boot/config/plugins/<?=$plugin?>/start-panel.sh">

_(LCD brightness, %)_:
: <input type="number" name="BRIGHTNESS" min="5" max="100" step="1" value="<?=htmlspecialchars($val('BRIGHTNESS','75'))?>">

_(Stats refresh, seconds)_:
: <input type="number" name="INTERVAL" min="1" max="10" step="1" value="<?=htmlspecialchars($val('INTERVAL','1'))?>">

_(Auto-rotate pages every)_:
: <select name="ROTATE"><?php opts([0=>'Off',10=>'10 seconds',20=>'20 seconds',30=>'30 seconds',60=>'60 seconds'], $val('ROTATE','0')); ?></select>

_(Screen off after idle)_:
: <select name="SCREEN_OFF_MIN"><?php opts([0=>'Never',1=>'1 minute',5=>'5 minutes',15=>'15 minutes'], $val('SCREEN_OFF_MIN','0')); ?></select>

_(Night mode &mdash; clamp brightness to 15%)_:
: <select name="NIGHT"><?php opts([0=>'Off',1=>'On'], $val('NIGHT','0')); ?></select>

_(Front-panel LEDs)_:
: <select name="LEDS"><?php opts([1=>'On',0=>'Off'], $val('LEDS','1')); ?></select>

_(Primary network interface &mdash; shown on Overview &amp; Home)_:
: <select name="PRIMARY_IFACE">
  <option value=""<?=$val('PRIMARY_IFACE','')===''?' selected':''?>>Auto (default route)</option>
  <?php foreach ($ifaces as $n) echo '<option value="' . htmlspecialchars($n) . '"' . ($val('PRIMARY_IFACE','') === $n ? ' selected' : '') . '>' . htmlspecialchars($n) . '</option>'; ?>
  </select>

&nbsp;
: <span class="buttons-spaced"><input type="submit" value="_(Apply)_"><input type="button" value="_(Done)_" onclick="done()"></span>
</form>

> Changes are written to the plugin's `settings.cfg` and the dashboard restarts to
> apply them. The same settings are editable live from the panel's own **SETTINGS**
> page.
